sequenceDiagram
    participant NMS as Network Management System
    participant Poller as SNMP Poller
    participant Agent as SNMP Agent
    participant UPF as UPF
    participant DB as Time-Series Database

    loop Every 30 seconds
        NMS->>Poller: Schedule Polling
        Poller->>Agent: SNMP GET Requests
        Agent->>UPF: Collect Metrics
        UPF-->>Agent: Metric Values
        Agent-->>Poller: SNMP Responses
        Poller->>DB: Store Metrics
        DB-->>Poller: Confirmation
        Poller-->>NMS: Polling Results
    end

    NMS->>DB: Query Historical Data
    DB-->>NMS: Time-Series Data
    NMS->>NMS: Generate Reports/Dashboards

    style NMS fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#333
    style Poller fill:#e8f5e8,stroke:#333
    style Agent fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#333
    style UPF fill:#f1f8e9,stroke:#333
    style DB fill:#e0f2f1,stroke:#333